osad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLingu規模細學生少排名低姐，但都係UGC學術資格<br />\n私立U點比到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:26:57.000Z","msg":"um 據我所知 真心 hsu好好多"},{"pid":"f28a239e27de2c6bd4352d617ec14d87edfb7081","tid":1982104,"uid":51200,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"fac7eafa97e5487ecbe5763eafd75f3eca055f17","tid":1982104,"uid":185710,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5272e34f05e3e80f7584ca42cd1fdc2f49fcc030","tid":1982104,"uid":51200,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a2fdf84323e23376088b5ac63c4b62a3ceedc203","tid":1982104,"uid":278103,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"如果計出路，資源，係咪hsu 會好啲？而lingu個優勢係ugc？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"邊一忽令你覺得資源同出路會係HSU好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個因果關係係咪搞錯咗<br />\n<br />\nUGC你唔好理邊間<br />\n香港求其一間嘅資源都屌打私立大學幾個double啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLingu規模細學生少排名低姐，但都係UGC學術資格<br />\n私立U點比到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:26:57.000Z","msg":"um 據我所知 真心 hsu好好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T21:01:44.000Z","msg":"唔好就咁一句就算<br />\nLingu BBA有ranking架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，雖然都係垃圾<br />\n商學院D專業認證高好多<br />\n而且UGC scholarship&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;私立大學<br />\n<br />\n抄WIKI，淨係引用同BBA 有關嘅<br />\n<br />\n1） 嶺大商學院亦為國際商管學院促進協會(AACSB)認證成員，是世界頂尖5%的商學院之一。在香港八間有開設商學院的法定大學當中，有七間有AACSB認證，因此在設有商學院的法定大學當中只有一間院校未能取得相關認證。<br />\n<br />\nHSU佢申請左差唔多七年，請埋鬼佬做院長都未申請到AACSB<br />\n<br />\n2）2017年，嶺大金融學科進入ARWU第151-200位[8]，管理學科進入世界三百強。<br />\n<br />\n3）2018年，嶺大商學院的工商管理（榮譽）學士 - AAcSB風險及保險管理課程獲國際保險學會頒發2018年度「全球優秀保險學科」，成為該年度全球九所得獎院校之一。<br />\n<br />\n4) 嶺大申請的「優配研究金」項目，在八間資助院校之中排行第二<br />\n<br />\n5) Exchange 比率最高9成，資助比率八大最高<br />\n<br />\n質保局係90年代已經確保左UGC公立大學嘅教育質素同學術水平要一致<br />\n而私立大學把尺無論喺研究或者教育質素，都低過UGC，<br />\n政府之前係樹仁評審嘅時候講嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUGC既Research funding 又前私立大學好多馬鼻<br />\nLingu政府經常性撥備丶補助金丶綜合資源撥備，按人頭計，同其他八大差唔多<br />\n同OU/HSU呢啲差好遠<br />\n係香港，UGC同非UGC係兩個等級黎<br />\n<br />\n嶺南已經係廢，要搞博雅教育去爭finding <br />\n但講funding 私立大學真係冇得比<br />\n<br />\n利申 中過伏入所謂香港私立大學，好彩tran到U，嗰時啲同學個個都有yr 1就爭tran，City 最易，位又多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73783d2803cec07325e8112841c34b0974754e9a","tid":1982104,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f28a239e27de2c6bd4352d617ec14d87edfb7081","tid":1982104,"uid":51200,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"fac7eafa97e5487ecbe5763eafd75f3eca055f17","tid":1982104,"uid":185710,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5272e34f05e3e80f7584ca42cd1fdc2f49fcc030","tid":1982104,"uid":51200,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"邊一忽令你覺得資源同出路會係HSU好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個因果關係係咪搞錯咗<br />\n<br />\nUGC你唔好理邊間<br />\n香港求其一間嘅資源都屌打私立大學幾個double啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLingu規模細學生少排名低姐，